description:
关于提高社区开发成员积极性的提案

由于 48Club 业务生态体系的完善，开发团队面临的问题也会越来越多，任何审计都有可能遗漏的问题，我提议

1. 针对于社区反馈的 BUG, 根据性质给予首位反馈的用户进行奖励;
2. 对于 48Club 开源项目做出贡献的用户(BUG 修复, 新特性贡献);

奖励(由 48Club 俱乐部赞助)具体金额由 48Club 理事或开发团队讨论后给予发放。


社区将牢记每一份来自社区成员的贡献，并且会奖励每一位贡献者。

-----------------------------------------------------------

Proposal on increasing the enthusiasm of community development members

As the 48Club business ecosystem improves, the development team will face more and more problems. Any audit may miss problems. I propose

1. For bugs reported by the community, rewards will be given to the first user to provide feedback according to the nature;
2. Users who contribute to the 48Club open source project (bug fixes, new feature contributions);

The specific amount of the reward (sponsored by 48Club) will be distributed after discussion by the 48Club directors or development team.


The community will remember every contribution from community members and will reward every contributor.
